body:
This branch has:
- a modified version of `Configuration/PyReleaseValidation/python/relval_steps.py` for using the gen-sim produced in `CMSSW_7_1_14` and for using by default the BS for nominal collisions 2015 (originally in #7904 with a fix); 
- a modified version of `Configuration/AlCa/python/autoCond.py` for using the GTs for Run2 simulations in 25 and 50 ns with the new BS (originally in #7904);
- a modified version of `Configuration/AlCa/python/autoCond.py` for using the GTs for Run1 simulations with more realistic tracker material budget SIM geometry;
- a modified version of `Configuration/StandardSequences/python/VtxSmeared.py` for using the `VtxSmearedDefaultKey` for `NominalCollisions2015` (originally in #7904).
